4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who want to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will acquire a strong foundation in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration. Key skills taught include cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis, alongside risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Successful graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop